elements.name: Como usuario verifico que el post esté creado y luego eliminado

steps.name: I wait for a signal containing "logged" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "posting" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post created" for 30 seconds
I select the post with title "$$name_1"
I send a signal to user 1 containing "checking post"
I send a signal to user 1 containing "checked post"
I wait for a signal containing "deleting" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post deleted" for 30 seconds
I check page does not exist

name: Crear un post y que este sea visible para el usuario, eliminarlo y que el usuario deje de verlo
